body:
Those are just warning messages. Not error messages. Everything seems to be working as expected.
You can try creating a different folder and creating your pip package there.
Or you can simply try running
```
bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/build_pip_package .
```
Which should create the whl file in the folder you are running the command in.
